{"id":"naarai","term":"Naarai","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Youthful, a military chief in David’s army (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:37\">1 Chr. 11:37</a>), called also Paarai (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:35\">2 Sam. 23:35</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 11:37","2 Samuel 23:35"]}